Clarice M. Starling.

1222
01:50:54,003 --> 01:50:55,421
- Congratulations.
- Thank you.

1223
01:51:08,977 --> 01:51:11,187
Ernest W. Stevens.

1224
01:51:29,747 --> 01:51:33,102
- Special Agent Starling.
- Oh, Special Agent Mapp.

1225
01:51:33,126 --> 01:51:35,729
- Phone call.
- Oh, thank you. Excuse me, gentlemen.

1226
01:51:35,753 --> 01:51:36,754
Starling?

1227
01:51:39,757 --> 01:51:42,194
Pilch. Would you take our picture?

1228
01:51:42,218 --> 01:51:43,428
Sure.

1229
01:51:45,263 --> 01:51:47,265
Look, I just wanted to say
congratulations.

1230
01:51:48,433 --> 01:51:51,936
And I'm not much good at this kind of
thing, so I'm gonna duck outta here.

1231
01:51:52,520 --> 01:51:54,147
Okay. Sure. Um -

1232
01:51:55,356 --> 01:51:57,191
Thank you, Mr. Crawford.

1233
01:52:00,737 --> 01:52:01,737
Um-

1234
01:52:05,074 --> 01:52:07,243
Your father would've been proud today.

1235
01:52:10,246 --> 01:52:11,914
Don't forget your phone call.

1236
01:52:16,961 --> 01:52:17,962
Starling.

1237
01:52:18,504 --> 01:52:20,131
<i>Well, Clarice.</i>

1238
01:52:20,715 --> 01:52:23,235
Have the lambs stopped screaming?

1239
01:52:23,259 --> 01:52:26,071
<i>- Dr. Lester.
- Don't bother with a trace.</i>

1240
01:52:26,095 --> 01:52:27,972
I won't be on long enough.

1241
01:52:31,142 --> 01:52:32,894
Where are you, Dr. Lecter?

1242
01:52:33,728 --> 01:52:35,873
I have no plans to call on you, Clarice.

1243
01:52:35,897 --> 01:52:38,358
The world's more interesting
with you in it.

1244
01:52:38,941 --> 01:52:42,087
<i>So you take care now
to extend me the same courtesy.</i>

1245
01:52:42,111 --> 01:52:44,113
You know I can't make that promise.

1246
01:52:44,697 --> 01:52:47,450
I do wish we could chat longer, but...

1247
01:52:48,785 --> 01:52:51,037
I'm having an old friend for dinner.

1248
01:52:52,747 --> 01:52:53,831
Bye.

1249
01:52:54,665 --> 01:52:55,750
<i>Dr. Lecter!</i>

1250
01:52:58,378 --> 01:52:59,462
Dr. Lecter?

1251
01:53:02,173 --> 01:53:03,257
Dr. Lecter?

1252
01:53:05,635 --> 01:53:06,761
Dr. Lecter?

1253
01:53:07,637 --> 01:53:09,472
Very important -
Oh, excuse me. I'm sorry.

1254
01:53:10,056 --> 01:53:12,701
- Is the security system all set up?
- Oh, yeah, the big-shot security.

1255
01:53:12,725 --> 01:53:14,268
Oh, thank you. I appreciate that.

